snippet.title: Season 2 Multiplayer Launch Trailer | Call of Duty: Warzone & Modern Warfare III
snippet.description:
The strong survive. The strongest win 💀

Outlast the living and the dead on three new 6v6 maps, the Zombie-filled Hordepoint mode, and more in Season 2 of #MW3 on February 7.

Follow #CallofDuty for the latest intel:
